A new species of the genus Megapomponia Boulard (Hemiptera: Cicadidae) from southern Vietnam, with a revised key to the species of MegapomponiaA new cicada species, Megapomponia macilenta Lee, sp. nov., is described from Thu Dau Mot, southern Vietnam. Information on geographic distributions of and a revised key to the species of the genus Megapomponia Boulard are provided.